        FW["Firewall Rule
─────────────────────────
Allow internal traffic
Source CIDR: 10.0.0.0/20
Destination: 10.0.0.0/20
Protocol: all"]:::fwStyle

        subgraph SUBNET["  Subnet: databricks-vpc-subnet  "]
